7/T%C3%ADch-Th%E1%BA%A3o-l%C4%A9nh/poem-HES416YUZEdnq3iZVa6sYw">Tích Thảo lĩnh - 積草嶺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-V%C4%A9nh/Tr%C3%BA-d%E1%BA%A1-l%E1%BA%A1c-%E1%BB%A8c-bi%E1%BB%87t/poem-A1qWp2TVE713T9GYde49XQ">Trú dạ lạc - Ức biệt - 晝夜樂－憶別</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-V%C4%A9nh/author-ODOFEl8xHVsWXQUPgj9Ktg">Liễu Vĩnh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/T%E1%BB%B1-c%E1%BB%95-ch%C6%B0-tri%E1%BA%BFt-nh%C3%A2n/poem-AcafTrS8O_a9zrO1myLsZg">Tự cổ chư triết nhân - 自古諸哲人</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/author-o98HuijKnTRKdgvHyXbEYw">Hàn Sơn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Quy-M%C3%B4ng/T%E1%BB%AD-D%E1%BA%A1-bi%E1%BA%BFn-ca-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-vsLeaN4JibJG8YUXj17FOQ">Tử Dạ biến ca kỳ 1 - 子夜變歌其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Quy-M%C3%B4ng/author-FCMLXx_iJwv1UkwFEUT-cw">Lục Quy Mông</a>)<br></div>	</div>
